snippet.title: Pocket City Official Release Trailer [iOS & Android]
snippet.description:
Become mayor and build a city! Pocket City is an ambitious new city building game for iOS and Android, available now. No microtransactions or annoying timers! Pocket City aims to capture the fun of city building on mobile without IAPs. 

iOS: https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/pocket-city/id1330451888?mt=8
Android: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.codebrewgames.pocketcitygame&hl=en_US

Check out more at https://pocketcitygame.com
